title: 820-3476 Chager Phase Voltage Short to ground
message: Hi Guys i'm working on a 820-3476 board getting a short to ground on pin 1 of F7140 tried to inject voltage to find the short but nothing. All i notice is that its only getting 4 volts to ppbus system any ideas on what the problem can be?

title: 820-3476 Chager Phase Voltage Short to ground
message: Inject voltage, is the CPU getting warm?

title: 820-3476 Chager Phase Voltage Short to ground
message: i injected 12 volts at pin 1 nothing happens cpu did not get warm it uses all current  but nothing gets hot my max current setting is 5.1 amps on my power supply.

title: 820-3476 Chager Phase Voltage Short to ground
message: No idea, you are putting 5A into the board, something must get warm or it is a hard 0 Ohm short inside the board.
